  arxiv       = {2509.21035},
  preview     = {clause.png},
  abstract    = {CLAUSE is a three-agent neuro-symbolic framework that treats knowledge-graph context construction as a budgeted sequential decision process. Using the proposed LC-MAPPO (Lagrangian-Constrained Multi-Agent PPO), a Subgraph Architect, Path Navigator and Context Curator are jointly optimized under per-query budgets on edge edits, interaction steps and selected tokens.},
